Carolyn Green, Vice President - Government Affairs, has advised us of her
resignation from Enron Corp. effective Friday ) August 4, 2000.  Carolyn is
pursuing an opportunity with Sunoco, Inc. as their Vice President for Health,
Environment and Safety and will be making Philadelphia her new home base.
We want to thank Carolyn for her hard work and many contributions to Azurix
and Enron.  Please join me in wishing Carolyn the very best in her new
venture.

